--- Astrotrain / Soundwave ---

Astrotrain turns to Cyclonus, "Yah, we're going to pick up some 
new bots." Astroblast moves away from Wildrider and Cyclonus, 
and transforms into spaceship mode. His hatch opens, "Wildrider, 
get in. Cyclonus, we leave now?"

-----------------------------

Soundwave nods, thinks to himself <<foolish braggart, I follow my 
own agenda, and it would be interesting to see a fight between 
Megatron and Havotron>> and says, "As it should be, Havotron."
